    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/c72449466ee659fc5e7af406d679f1b2.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/c72449466ee659fc5e7af406d679f1b2.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/c72449466ee659fc5e7af406d679f1b2.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🚀<strong> UNIQUE BOOMERANG MECHANIC!</strong> Think outside the box to both move your character and aim and throw your boomerang at the same time to interact with the game's varied mechanics. You've never played a platformer quite like this.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🌌<strong> Enjoy a sci-fi story about disability told from a person who's seen it first hand.</strong> Never interrupting gameplay, but provoking deep thoughts in-between levels.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/0bebe9e475addeff7646a16d16212fc8.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/0bebe9e475addeff7646a16d16212fc8.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/0bebe9e475addeff7646a16d16212fc8.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🧠<strong> Chase times on online leaderboards</strong> with Sophia's intuitive, multi-layered, and skill expressive moveset!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🍪<strong> Collect cookies and cosmetics. Discover secrets.</strong> More than 100 tasty collectables are waiting. Use them to upgrade your fashion. But they are not the only secrets on this planet...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🏃‍♀️<strong> Fight bosses, run for your life.</strong> The end of (almost) every level holds a challenge. 3 Bosses to defeat and a lot of deadly traps to avoid.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/6e5109aa690b88d58c0668cfb3027b2a.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/6e5109aa690b88d58c0668cfb3027b